Thanks, Marcus! So, just to confirm, we have:

- Two Classic Burgers, cooked medium, with lettuce wraps and two side salads
- One Vegetable Stir Fry with cauliflower rice

That sounds delicious! 

Would you like anything to drink with your order? We have some great options like Coca-Cola, Fresh Orange Juice, or maybe a Cappuccino if you're in the mood for coffee!
name: order_taking_llm
